title: Seafolly Women's Dd Cup Double Wrap Front Bra Bikini Top Swimsuit
features: FOR MORE OPTIONS - Click the SEAFOLLY link above for more from our full collection of swimwear, cover ups and kids swimwear. Search Amazon for "Seafolly Eco Collective" for more from this collection.

ABOUT SEAFOLLY - We’re Australia’s leader in swimwear, born and worn since 1975. We believe great fit is a feeling; it frees you to do more and be more, in swimwear and cover-ups made to last and love. Our design inspiration comes from our active, carefree Australian beach culture. Every piece is fitted and tested on real women and it shows. SEAFOLLY'S product quality is at the heart of what makes us different.

ECO FRIENDLY FABRIC - This style is made with fibers made from recycled materials so you can rest easy knowing you’re doing your part. Not only has this environmentally responsible new fabric recycled industrial waste, it has helped offset the need for new resources such as petroleum and reduced greenhouse gas emissions. Support us as we work to a more sustainable SEAFOLLY.

FIT - At SEAFOLLY we believe fit a feeling not a size. All our swimwear is designed in Australia. We fit every single piece on real women on a multitude of body shapes. We thoroughly test our fabrics to ensure they will last without stretching, sagging or fading over time. All our tops and bottoms are made to love and last. With design details that ensure a superior fit, we inspire confidence when it matters most.

STYLE FEATURES -Wrap front detail for extra coverage, quick dry soft cups for shape and support. Side boning for shape definition. Adjustable straps covert to cross back style for fit versatility. Multi-fit Adjustable e-hook for the perfect fit.
description: Since 1975, Seafolly has been at the epicenter of Australian beach lifestyle and has quickly become one of the most recognized swimwear and beach lifestyle brands world-wide. Inspired by endless summer days, the Seafolly collection of women's and girl’s swimwear, cover ups, activewear eyewear and accessories radiate the warmth of the Australian beach lifestyle. Soak in light-filled days with prints and colors that illuminate the skin. Glow in new Seafolly swimwear in the mid-summer noon or beat the heat in our water-loving active pieces. It’s time to tip toward the sun. It’s time to shine in Seafolly. Seafolly is proud to be a member of the Ethical Trading Initiative (ETI).
